  "detailed_description": "Immerse yourself in the world of Japanese beautiful places / towns for about 20 minutes.<br />\r\nYou will find japanese ladies, streets, towns and gardens.<br />\r\nThere is not much interactivity, so you can't grab things at the moment. It is a tour.<br />\r\nEnjoy 20 minutes walk in Japan!<br />\r\nIn the game, you will be able to move freely, enter open rooms, visit the streets, towns and temples, to achieve a relaxing and enjoyable walking tour.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nInstructions:<br />\r\nMovement: The trigger button of the right controller for movement; press the touchpad of the right controller to turn left and right.<br />\r\nMENU: Menu button on the left controller for menu; press trigger button of the left controller to selcect.",
  "about_the_game": "Immerse yourself in the world of Japanese beautiful places / towns for about 20 minutes.<br />\r\nYou will find japanese ladies, streets, towns and gardens.<br />\r\nThere is not much interactivity, so you can't grab things at the moment. It is a tour.<br />\r\nEnjoy 20 minutes walk in Japan!<br />\r\nIn the game, you will be able to move freely, enter open rooms, visit the streets, towns and temples, to achieve a relaxing and enjoyable walking tour.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nInstructions:<br />\r\nMovement: The trigger button of the right controller for movement; press the touchpad of the right controller to turn left and right.<br />\r\nMENU: Menu button on the left controller for menu; press trigger button of the left controller to selcect.",
